Please note that this is a *very* rough first commit...it works, on my machine, but 
it is not well-tested. YMMV. Reasonable documentation is still some ways off, I'm afraid.

You'll need to intall CouchDB, a noSQL database; you can also use Cloudant 
(http://www.cloudant.com), which offers CouchDB as an Amazon-hosted service.

You'll need to replace "<key>" with your consumer API key in  
Backtweets/TermSearch.php and Mendeley/ArticleStats.php. 



